(283, 3, '2019-03-25 15:29:59', '2019-03-25 15:29:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">Peru is a country that falls in love with the incredible contrasts of its culture, destinations and landscapes. The reasons to visit it are many and here we tell you! Its gastronomy: Peru has been considered the best culinary destination in the world according to the World Travel Awards, thanks to its so rich and diverse cuisine that stands out for the combination of fruits, vegetables and fish, offering many options of aromas and flavors to enjoy. Ceviche and its typical dish known as ají de gallina, are very popular. You can not stop trying them!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":298} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" class=\"wp-image-298\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>His landscapes: If what you are looking for during your vacations is to change the environment and discover incredible places, Peru is your destination! One of its most impressive attractions is the Machu Picchu, an ancient Inca citadel considered one of the ten wonders of the modern world. This is the most important work for the Incas, built on a mountain, based on stones that were carved with great precision and detail.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":297} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-2-Copy-413x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" class=\"wp-image-297\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Their crafts: If you are one of the travelers that enjoys buying souvenirs of your trip, the crafts of Peru will enchant you! These products, handmade by their inhabitants, perfectly represent their art, history and culture.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":296} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-3-Copy-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" class=\"wp-image-296\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Are you already convinced? Know the best options to travel to Peru here -&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Why should you include Peru in your next vacation?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-should-you-include-peru-in-your-next-vacation', '', '', '2019-03-25 15:32:01', '2019-03-25 15:32:01', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=283', 0, 'post', '', 0);
