(293, 3, '2019-03-25 15:39:21', '2019-03-25 15:39:21', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">A region of incredible contrasts, where you find a wide cultural, natural, historical, gastronomic and landscape diversity. In Latin America, the adventures are endless! 1. You can explore ancient and millenary cities, fruit of the civilizations that reigned for years before the arrival of the Spanish.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":308} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" class=\"wp-image-308\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2- You will have the opportunity to navigate the largest, most impressive, deepest and widest river in the world: the Amazon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":309} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" class=\"wp-image-309\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3- You can taste Colombian coffee, considered by many to be the best in the world, thanks to its quality and authentic flavor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":305} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" class=\"wp-image-305\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4- You will enjoy a rich and exotic gastronomy that goes from the Peruvian ceviche, to the delicious Colombian paisa tray.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":304} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-4-Copy-289x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" class=\"wp-image-304\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do you want to live uniq