(300, 3, '2019-03-25 15:47:18', '2019-03-25 15:47:18', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">The Colombian capital is a city with a lot to offer, its cultural diversity, nightlife, museums, its pleasant average temperature of 14 ° C and its modern and colonial buildings, make it one of the most visited destinations in the country.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":310} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-1-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" class=\"wp-image-310\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Cerro de Monserrate is one of the main attractions of the city, which can be climbed by funicular, cable car or walking, above you can find the Sanctuary of the fallen Lord, the viewpoint that offers a wonderful view, restaurants of Colombian food and sale of crafts and typical products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":319} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-319\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the other hand, in the Historic Center of La Candelaria, there are important museums, where you can admire paintings by Botero and Picasso, as well as incredible pieces of gold. In this area, you can also visit the Plaza de Bolívar, built since 1539 and which is surrounded by important public buildings and tourist and historical points of interest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":318} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-3-Copy-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" class=\"wp-image-318\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Its commercial area offers a wide variety of options in clothing stores, footwear, accessories, jewelry, technology, antiques and crafts, to bring your best memory of Colombia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":317} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-4-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"boogota\" class=\"wp-image-317\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You will also find the famous Zona G, which is one of the most exclusive in the city and has become the favorite place for travelers looking to enjoy a wide variety of cuisine, as it has a large number of restaurants of all kinds. Image 5 And you, when are you coming to enjoy this city charm? Know all your travel options here -&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Bogotá, a destination you can not miss!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bogota-a-destination-you-can-not-miss', '', '', '2019-03-25 15:55:17', '2019-03-25 15:55:17', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=300', 0, 'post', '', 0),
