(321, 3, '2019-03-25 17:59:44', '2019-03-25 17:59:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">Medellin is a destination full of flowers, colors, flavors and innovation and has become the favorite city of thousands of tourists who have cataloged it on the TripAdvisor platform as the best tourist destination in South America, making it worthy of the \"Traveler\'s Choice\" award. The mixture between the colonial past and the innovativeness of the city, makes it a tourist attraction recognized worldwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":314} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" class=\"wp-image-314\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is known as the \"city of eternal spring\" thanks to its pleasant average climate of 24 ° C, its famous flower fair, gardens, parks and the mountain landscapes that surround it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":313} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" class=\"wp-image-313\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Medellin is always ready to surprise its visitors! Do not miss visiting it and plan your trip here -&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Discover Medellin, the best tourist destination in South America', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'discover-medellin-the-best-tourist-destination-in-south-america', '', '', '2019-03-25 17:59:47', '2019-03-25 17:59:47', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=321', 0, 'post', '', 0),
