(329, 3, '2019-03-25 18:07:18', '2019-03-25 18:07:18', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">科科拉 山 谷是一 个美丽 的自然景 观，位于哥 伦比亚Quindío山脉以及安第斯山脉中央山脉的山谷中，是咖啡区最杰出的旅游胜地之一。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":312} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-312\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>它以奇特的绿色山脉和繁茂的植被著称，在这里被发现的哥伦比亚国家树“拉帕尔马德塞拉”，高达60米，遍布整个山群。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":320} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"vlle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-320\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Orejiamarillos鹦鹉以及其他濒危动物在这些树上生活并繁殖。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":311} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-311\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>毫无疑问，科科拉山谷是山脉、动物群、棕榈树、河流、雾和大自然的完美结合…不要错过去了解它的机会-&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '科科 拉  山 谷，一个自 然旅行 爱好者的理想的目的地', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e7%a7%91%e7%a7%91-%e6%8b%89-%e5%b1%b1-%e8%b0%b7%ef%bc%8c%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e8%87%aa-%e7%84%b6%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c-%e7%88%b1%e5%a5%bd%e8%80%85%e7%9a%84%e7%90%86%e6%83%b3%e7%9a%84%e7%9b%ae%e7%9a%84', '', '', '2019-03-25 18:09:10', '2019-03-25 18:09:10', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=329', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(330, 3, '2019-03-25 18:09:07', '2019-03-25 18:09:07', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">科科拉 山 谷是一 个美丽 的自然景 观，位于哥 伦比亚Quindío山脉以及安第斯山脉中央山脉的山谷中，是咖啡区最杰出的旅游胜地之一。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":312} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-312\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>它以奇特的绿色山脉和繁茂的植被著称，在这里被发现的哥伦比亚国家树“拉帕尔马德塞拉”，高达60米，遍布整个山群。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":320} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"vlle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-320\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Orejiamarillos鹦鹉以及其他濒危动物在这些树上生活并繁殖。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":311} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" class=\"wp-image-311\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>毫无疑问，科科拉山谷是山脉、动物群、棕榈树、河流、雾和大自然的完美结合…不要错过去了解它的机会-&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '科科 拉  山 谷，一个自 然旅行 爱好者的理想的目的地', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '329-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 18:09:07', '2019-03-25 18:09:07', '', 329, 'https://new.anditrip.com/329-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(331, 3, '2019-03-25 18:12:31', '2019-03-25 18:12:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">This country located northwest of the continent of South America, has a wide variety of tourist destinations rich in nature, culture and history. Here we tell you 4 great reasons why you should include Colombia in your next vacation -&gt; 1. The charisma of its people. Being one of the happiest countries in the world, Colombians live full of joy that spreads, its inhabitants have a mixture of traits, races, accents and always receive a smile to everyone who visits their land.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":356} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" class=\"wp-image-356\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. The climate and its landscapes. Here the temperatures are as diverse as the landscapes, where you can find from modern and colonial cities, to natural forests, savannas, deserts, wetlands, páramos and the largest river in the world, the Amazon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":357} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-2-Copy-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" class=\"wp-image-357\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Its architecture. In this country everything is beautiful and varied, in its architecture you can see from buildings and innovative structures such as Medellin and Bogota, to facades full of history and colonial charm such as Cartagena.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":358} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" class=\"wp-image-358\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4- Your coffee. Famous for its flavor and quality, Colombia is positioned among the main countries producing soft coffee in the world. Its coffee landscapes were declared a World Heritage Site by Unesco and offer a unique combination of its culture and tradition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":359} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-4-Copy-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" class=\"wp-image-359\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You already have enough reasons to come to Colombia! Know all our travel options here -&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Colombia, a country full of flavor.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'colombia-a-country-full-of-flavor', '', '', '2019-03-25 18:12:33', '2019-03-25 18:12:33', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=331', 0, 'post', '', 0),
