(351, 3, '2019-03-25 18:36:56', '2019-03-25 18:36:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Music transmits emotions, melodies awaken sensations of joy, joy and even sadness, with sounds in harmony you can appreciate the cultural richness of a country, the traditions of each place, but also understand and observe how different a culture of culture can be. other. Travel to these musical places of South America and travel with all the senses, but above all the hearing, the melodies and experiences they offer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Explore the sensual rhythms of Tango in Argentina: Tango is a symbol of Argentina, it is a complex dance with sensual figures and movements, where the couple does not let go for a single moment. Although its beginnings were in the suburbs of the city, where people drowned their sorrows with sweeping lyrics over time evolved and became the music of all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Buenos Aires currently has approximately 200 places where you can dance or witness tango shows, who like this genre and dance has the possibility to dance, listen and learn in many places with different environments and characteristics. During the month of August the capital of Argentina is the headquarters of the Festival and World Tango Championship, with popular milongas and public concerts. Do you dare to explore the sensual rhythms of tango?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":487} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-1-Copy-1-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"cali\" class=\"wp-image-487\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Brazil dances to the rhythm of the Samba: This country is one of the most visited in Latin America, a very fun, happy place, full of parties, customs and dances, where music is very important in the popular culture of the country, being the samba the symbol of Brazilian identity. A genre whose melody is the mixture of African rhythms with the locals until it became a national icon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is the maximum musical expression of the country and if you visit Brazil any time of the year, it will be inevitable not to join the festivities and at the best rhythm of the samba to live a unique and unforgettable experience</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":488} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-2-Copy-1-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"cali\" class=\"wp-image-488\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cali, the capital of Salsa in Colombia: Salsa is the musical rhythm that represents and identifies the city of Cali, the sound, dancers and the history of this musical genre culturally marks the region. Cali is known as the World Capital of Salsa and it is not for less, in the city you can see great salsa shows, you will learn to dance this musical rhythm, there are more than 90 dance schools and about 115 thematic establishments, known as old-fashioned clubs where the oldest songs of this genre will transport you to the past and the salsotecas where the timpani rhythm and the trumpets do not stop sounding.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Visiting Cali and not being seduced by this rhythm is impossible, salsa is a tourist product of the region and this has made it a favorite destination for many travelers in the world. Do not overlook this destiny and dare to move your hips to the rhythm of salsa!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":489} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-3-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-489\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Destinations with lots of music and fun.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'destinations-with-lots-of-music-and-fun', '', '', '2019-03-25 18:37:00', '2019-03-25 18:37:00', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=351', 0, 'post', '', 0),
