(376, 3, '2019-03-25 19:03:57', '2019-03-25 19:03:57', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">Cradle of Fernando Botero, famed Colombian plastic artist, Medellín stands out as the ideal destination for people who appreciate art, innovation and also enjoy the pleasant mountain climate. Learn a little more about the city of the eternal spring of Colombia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":551} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-medellín-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" class=\"wp-image-551\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently, it has 197 zones with free internet connection 24/7, which makes it the most connected city in the whole country. It has the most complete and efficient public transport system, which makes moving around it fast and easy.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":552} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-medellín-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" class=\"wp-image-552\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Among its attractions, the Museum of Antioquia, located in the center of the city, contains artistic collections of national and international reference, including pre-Columbian art and ceramics, which attracts national and foreign tourists throughout the year.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":553} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3-medellín-Copy-383x220.jpeg\" alt=\"medellin\" class=\"wp-image-553\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Plaza Botero is an indispensable reference of the city, since it can be seen 23 sculptures of this artist, distributed in the 7000 square meters that compose it. Being of free access and permanent exhibition, it has become a meeting point and local pride.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Medellín, the city of innovation in Colombia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'medellin-the-city-of-innovation-in-colombia', '', '', '2019-03-25 19:03:59', '2019-03-25 19:03:59', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=376', 0, 'post', '', 0),
