(386, 3, '2019-03-25 19:18:02', '2019-03-25 19:18:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\"> Sao Paulo is the main economic center of Brazil and a great cultural center of Latin America.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":570} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-342x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" class=\"wp-image-570\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Around 46 cultural centers, 101 museums and 141 libraries make up the vast cultural offer that can be found in Sao Paulo, where together, with a lush artistic environment, world-class restaurants and luxurious hotels coexist, making it a destination that has nothing to envy for important cities in other continents.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":569} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" class=\"wp-image-569\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gastronomy is the protagonist in this unstoppable city. In addition to international and local restaurants, the recurring food fairs and food trucks are part of the options enjoyed by locals and foreigners, when it comes to delicious food.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":571} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-440x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" class=\"wp-image-571\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sao Paulo is the largest city in the southern hemisphere and, therefore, the largest city in Brazil, where the development has been vertiginous, but not for that reason, it stops having attractive spaces for outdoor recreation and encounter with nature.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":572} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" class=\"wp-image-572\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It has 111 parks distributed throughout the city, in addition to the zoo and aquarium, those are the alternatives that the Paulists and foreigners have to spend different moments of recreation.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do you want to know this exuberant city? Enter our website and learn more about this destination in Latin America -&gt; <a href=\"http://www.anditrip.com\">www.anditrip.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sao Paulo, the most cosmopolitan city', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sao-paulo-the-most-cosmopolitan-city', '', '', '2019-03-25 19:19:59', '2019-03-25 19:19:59', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=386', 0, 'post', '', 0);
