(391, 3, '2019-03-25 19:26:59', '2019-03-25 19:26:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">Landscapes that will be recorded in your memory.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":582} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-1-339x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-582\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also known as the jewel of the Pacific, Valparaíso has a varied of cultural activities and beautiful restaurants to offer, here you will always have something to do.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":583} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-1-392x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-583\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One option is to visit the Museum of Natural History of Valparaíso, where its extensive variety of flora and fauna, typical of the place, will leave you speechless, to contemplate a playful exhibition that marvels all who visit it. It is an awesome place!<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":580} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-1-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-580\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The architecture of the city center is a Historical Heritage of Humanity, its picturesque streets will make walking through them a journey in time. In the historic center of Valparaíso you will find a maze of houses with ocean view, whose facades of vibrant colors in contrast to the blue of the Pacific, create a charming atmosphere that attracts hundreds of tourists annually.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":581} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-581\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being a coastal city, you can not stop visiting its port and enjoy the fresh sea products that you can taste in some delicious dish. Commercial premises, restaurants or pubs where the bohemian and casual atmosphere reigns, are some of the alternatives that you can enjoy in this beautiful region of Chile, which awaits your visit.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Valparaíso, beauty of the Pacific.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'valparaiso-beauty-of-the-pacific', '', '', '2019-03-25 19:27:02', '2019-03-25 19:27:02', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=391', 0, 'post', '', 0),
