irtues to discover.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":608} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-5-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-608\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you go to Quito, you can not stop standing with one foot in each of the halves of the world. Visit this monument of 30 meters high that is built on the site where a French explorer calculated that passes the line of the equator, in the year 1736. A mandatory destination of Ecuador.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Quito, the city in the middle of the world', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '406-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 19:54:47', '2019-03-25 19:54:47', '', 406, 'https://new.anditrip.com/406-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(409, 3, '2019-03-25 19:54:47', '2019-03-25 19:54:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>这座城市的海拔有足足2580米，并且其所拥有的保存最完好的南美的历史中心在1998年被评为世界文化遗产之一。<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":609} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-4-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-609\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>最近几年，它的经济发展飞快，因此这个城市的旅游体验与基础建设得到了大幅度的提升。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":606} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-4-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-606\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>它的高海拔使赋予了它稳定的山地气候，这让所有的游客都深深着迷。无处不在绿色植物以及善良朴实的人们，都让这个城市熠熠生辉。<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":607} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-4-326x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-607\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>卡罗琳娜植物园以及盆栽博物馆只是这个城市游览点的一小部分，这难道不棒吗？<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":610} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-4-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-610\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>如果你去基多，你的两只脚随时随地都踩在地球的分界线上。您也可以参观这个30米高的纪念碑——它建造在一名法国探险家于1736年测量赤道时所在的位置上，这也是基多的一个非去不可的景点。<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":608} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-5-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-608\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', '基多——世界中间的城市', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%9f%ba%e5%a4%9a-%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e4%b8%ad%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82', '', '', '2019-03-25 19:56:58', '2019-03-25 19:56:58', '', 0, 'http://new.anditrip.com/?p=409', 0, 'post', '', 0),
